Privacy Policy for Coffee Wonders

Effective Date: July 27, 2025

At Coffee Wonders, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, share, and safeguard your data when you use our mobile application ("App"). By using the App, you agree to the terms of this policy.

1. Information We Collect

We collect information to provide and improve your shopping experience. The types of information we collect include:


Personal Information

Account Information: When you sign up or sign in, we collect your email address and encrypted password.

Profile Details: You may choose to add, view, or edit your name, email, phone number, address, and profile picture in the Profile Details screen within the Account tab. Profile picture updates are managed via our website.

Order Information: When you place an order, we collect your address and the other information like your name, email, and phone number.e.g., we collect from your details that you already added in the Profile Details screen within the Account tab, to facilitate delivery.

Order History: Details of your past orders, including products purchased and order dates.


Non-Personal Information

Cart and Favorites: Products you add to your cart or mark as favorites are stored locally on your device using Hive.

Usage Data: Anonymized data about how you interact with the App (e.g., searches, page views) to enhance performance.

Language Preferences: The app is currently available in Arabic.


Locally Stored Data

Cart and favorites are stored on your device and are not sent to our servers unless you place an order.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:

Create and manage your account for secure sign-in using your email and password.

Allow you to add, view, or update your name, email, phone number, and address in the Profile Details screen within the Account tab.

Facilitate updates to your profile picture or password by prompting you to visit our secure website (https://coffee-wonders.com). The App will ask for your confirmation before navigating to the website, as these updates are not available in the App.

Process and deliver your orders using Cash on Delivery for now, may integrate payment gateway in the future.

Allow you to save products in your cart or favorites for quick access.

Display order history and user details in the Account screen.

Analyze anonymized usage data to improve the App’s functionality.


3. How We Share Your Information

We only share your information when necessary:

Delivery Partners: We share your name, address, and phone number with couriers to deliver your orders.

Website Updates: If you choose to update your profile picture or password, you will be directed to our secure website (https://coffee-wonders.com), where your data is processed securely.

Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect our rights.

No Financial Data: Since we currently use Cash on Delivery, we do not collect or share payment information. In the future, we plan to integrate payment gateway for additional payment options, and we will update this policy accordingly.

We do not sell your personal information to third parties.


4. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your data:

Encryption: API communications and website interactions use HTTPS to secure data in transit.

Local Storage: Cart and favorites data is stored securely on your device using Hive, protected by your device’s security features.

Website Security: Updates to your profile picture or password on our website are protected by industry-standard security practices.

Limitations: While we strive to protect your data, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure. Please use the App and website responsibly.


5. Your Rights

You have rights over your personal data, including:

Access: Request a copy of the data we hold about you.

Correction: Add, view, or update your name, email, phone number, or address in the Profile Details screen within the Account tab. To update your profile picture or password, the App will prompt you to visit our website after your confirmation.

Deletion: Request deletion of your account and associated data by contacting us via link will be shown on app Google Play store listing and submit that you want to delete your Coffee Wonders app, and the application support will delete your account when see your response.

Objection: Object to certain data processing (e.g., analytics, if applicable).



6. Account Deletion

You can delete your account at any time by contacting us via link will be shown on app Google Play store listing. Upon deletion:

All personal data on our servers (e.g., email, name, address, phone number, order history, profile picture) will be permanently removed.

Locally stored data (cart, favorites) will be cleared from your device.


7. Third-Party Services

The App uses third-party services that may collect data:

Hive: Stores cart and favorites locally on your device.

APIs: Fetch product, category, and order data from our servers.

Delivery Partners.

Website: Our secure website (https://coffee-wonders.com) handles profile picture and password updates.

These services have their own privacy policies, which we recommend reviewing.

9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this policy to reflect changes in our practices, features, or legal requirements. Significant updates will be communicated via the App or email.

10. Contact Us

If you have questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us:

Email: info@carizmaelectric.com

Website: https://coffee-wonders.com

